release_note: Fixed a very annoying bug where the photo library would show up out of order. Other minor bug fixes and improvements. Thanks for continuing to support us! Please reach out if you have any questions or suggestions.

Fixes and improvements for our top issues. Fixed Crash when selecting the Imported Formulas Pack Fixed Crash when accessing the store Fixed paid packs not downloading correctly Fixed Restore All now working correctly.

Massive Under The Hood Update! iOS 14 Support We rebuilt our image processing engine from the ground up. Image issues and crashes are..... poof ....gone. Our photo picker has been rebuilt to handle larger libraries. No more lagging while scrolling or selecting images. We ve optimized the app. Scrolling should be smooth like peanut butter. Presets now work better and Formulas apply quicker to images. Thanks for your support and your patience! We are finishing new textures texture packs and brand new presets coming soon that we know you re going to love.

New Formula Pack: Mood Magic 24 new formulas that add a variety of unique color tones subtle accents and mood. You can find this pack in the Formulas Tab after importing an image. iPad iPhone Xs Max layout fixes.
New Formula Pack: Mood Magic 24 new formulas that add a variety of unique color tones subtle accents and mood! iPad iPhone Xs Max layout fixes.

This is an interface update for the new iPhones and small content update! We ve been working on a massive content release but wanted to address some critical issues and bugs. Full details listed below: Updated interface for iPhone X Xs and Xs Max Updated News Section New Updated Content: 2 new Grit Grain textures 2 new Light Leak overlays 2 New Formula Packs: Community Pack 1 Universal Formulas Pack New Guest Formula Pack from Allison Ferris Bug fixes Export resolution bug fix especially for newer devices running on iOS 12 Slowness on devices when editing applying formulas Fixed some strange texture renderings Support link bug fixes Share Sheet fixes Other improvements and fixes Thanks for all of your continued support! If you feel so inclined we appreciate reviews on the App Store. Please follow us on Instagram at mextures!

Fixed the bug where images went missing in the Library Picker New film presets interface in adjustments We are pretty excited about this! Your image is now shown with the film preset applied to the thumbnail. No more guessing how the preset will look on your photos. 5 New Film Presets. More subtle and focused on slight film shifts. New custom library picker Easier navigation and browsing through your images and albums. 2 new texture packs In the store Dust Dirt Subtle grunge pack to add a weathered water damaged effect to your photos. Light Leaks 4 Includes a diverse range of colorful light leaks. Great for color toning adding artifacts. Added 3D Touch to home screen icon for 6s 6s users Quickly add formulas edit from your library and check the news feed right from your home screen. Added an FAQ section to the settings as well as a new easy way to get in touch with support. Small visual changes improvements and bug fixes to the app.

2.1.1 addresses bug fixes for the store What s New in 2.1: Live Editing! See your changes in realtime as you adjust the opacity of layers and adjustment strengths. The large numbers that covered your beautiful pictures are gone so you can see your changes. Introducing the Mextures Store: New Textures and formulas delivered directly in the app. We re launching with five new products and more to come both free and paid : X Film Bundle Anomaly Bundle Intensity Bundle Atmospheric Bundle and The Outfitters Formula Pack. As a way to say thanks to all of you we are giving away one of the new bundles and the Outfitters Formula Pack for free. Each of the bundles includes a brand new texture pack coupled with a brand new formula pack! Redesigned News Section. Slightly redesigned home screen for easier navigation. What s Fixed: Performance improvements enhancements. Bug crash fixes. What s Planned: Updated interfaces for iPhone 6 iPhone 6 Other exciting features coming Thanks for all of your continued support! 2.0 Release! New Formula Sharing! Manage and share your formulas and import formulas from others with our new Formula Manager New Polish Finish your edits with Polish which includes: 25 film presets exposure contrast black and white saturation fade white balance tint shadow highlight and sharpen New Textures Updates to existing packs with 47 new hand picked textures including a gorgeous new Light Leaks 3 texture pack Updated Formulas New Guest Formulas: 17 total guest contributors for over 130 formulas. New Formula Packs: Black and White Destroyed Film Winter and Spring packs Graphic overhaul of the app for a more refined and visually enjoyable UI Faster processing of images Tons of bug fixes Thank you all so much for your continued support! If you enjoy this update we would love if you left a review! As always you can reach us personally on Instagram merekdavis or at mextures. Keep tagging mextures!

Fixes to the camera library! Your newest photos are displayed first instead of the oldest. NEW Fall Formula Pack! 12 new warm and vivid formulas created by the Mextures community that are perfect for your autumn imagery. Various bugs squashed and screws tightened within the app. As always thank you for your continued support! We have some really fun enhancements planned for an upcoming release. We also appreciate the feedback reviews. Please do not hesitate to contact us directly on Instagram mexturesapp merekdavis.

Graphic overhaul for iOS7 New Icon New revamped home screen Larger text for opacity slider Other iOS UI enhancements. New inspiration feed design We now have larger higher resolution images in the feed. iOS 7 bugs squashed. As always we appreciate the reviews ratings you leave for us. Be sure to follow us on Instagram for the latest updates and sneak peaks: MexturesApp MerekDavis That s also a great way to reach us personally for any questions!

New Free Mextures Pack The Radiance Pack with 11 new Mextures is what would happen if gradients and light leaks had a baby. Soft clean glows and vivid tones that will change the mood and vibe of any picture. They work great with any type of picture. We ve added a button to show the original image while you re editing! You can use it while browsing through formulas as well as in the Layers tab. Various bugs squashed and things fixed. Please be sure to rate Mextures if you are enjoying it and for the latest news and contests follow us on Instagram: MexturesApp and MerekDavis. Thanks for all your support! We re hard at work on the next update!

We finally fixed the saving of EXIF data and Geolocation once and for all. Your edits within Mextures will retain all geolocation and EXIF data. We re sorry for the mixup. We also crushed a bunch of crash issues and squashed a ton of bugs in this update. You should see Mextures running smoother than ever. If you do happen to have a crash please contact me directly at hello mextures.com so we can squash it together. Thanks so much for all your support and incredible fedback!

Images edited in Mextures now retain EXIF data when exported! We added a new Summer Formula Pack full of 9 subtle soft and warm edits. An all new Guest Formula Pack! You can now browse all Guest Formulas at once! You ll see the button under the Guest Formulas section. A few under the hood enhancements tweaks. Be sure to keep tagging your images with Mextures on Instagram Facebook and Twitter for a chance to get featured on our inspiration page!

What the Crop ! Having pixels taken away is no fun. We added the option to edit your photos non cropped in full resolution. Just select Don t Crop on the Crop Screen and voila! No more square photos! Coming Soon: Retain EXIF Geolocation info on export. More fun updates! Note: We know of a crash bug haunting 4g iPod Touches. We re working to get this fixed as quick as possible! Thanks for being patient. For other users experiencing a crash please restart your phone. If you still experience an issue please contact us directly at help mextures.com
